# Project Alchemist — root Cursor context

**[INIT]** TS/Next.js monorepo: NL → Serum **preset candidates** → rank → optional WASM **`.fxp`**. **Not** a C++/JUCE/AU plugin in this tree unless you open a **separate** DSP project.

**Stack:** `apps/web-app`, `packages/shared-engine`, `packages/shared-types`, optional Rust→WASM in `packages/fxp-encoder`.

## Truth sources (read before big edits)

- **`docs/FIRESTARTER.md`** — **recovery bible** / full orientation; **Doc logic** = FIRE vs FIRESTARTER; **Appendix A** workflow; **Appendix B** INIT; **Appendix C** optional agent checklist; **Appendix D** Aji notes. Under **`docs/`** only **FIRESTARTER** + **FIRE**. **Material** product edits land here first.
- **`docs/FIRE.md`** — **lightweight** assessment / LLM surface: §E–§L, **`verify_post_summary`**. **Metrics block:** **`pnpm fire:sync`** (after green verify) or **`ALCHEMIST_FIRE_SYNC=1`** — not a substitute for FIRESTARTER for implementation detail.
- **`docs/AIOM-Fused-Principles.md`** — AIOM **truth-matrix** snapshot vs **`live`** health, divergence, freshness; fuses external architecture review with Alchemist canon (**HARD GATE** still wins).
- **`.cursor/rules/alchemist-aiom-verification.mdc`** — always-on AIOM verification discipline (supplements brief; no gate math changes).
- **`.cursor/rules/alchemist-brief.mdc`** + **`alchemist-security-posture.mdc`** + **`alchemist-healthy-ai-environment.mdc`** + **`alchemist-dsp-vs-ts-gates.mdc`** + **`alchemist-role-mission.mdc`** + **`alchemist-inner-circle-default.mdc`** + **`alchemist-git-save-after-meta.mdc`** — always-on **security posture** (HARD GATE, keys, stub/prod parity, WASM, LLM boundaries, verify chain) + **healthy AI ops** (law vs model, honest capability, no shadow governance, provider/data hygiene) + guardrails + **Lead Architect** role / **`/plan`·`/fix`·`/refactor`·`/audit`** + **default Cursor chat tone** (English default; peer habits from **`.cursor/skills/inner-circle-voice/`**, after canon) + **commit/push after meta edits** (`git-save` or generic git; see **`docs/cursor-universal-habits.md`** for **User Rules** on other machines/repos).
- **`research/README.md`** + **`alchemist-aji-fluidic.mdc`** (scoped) — optional **Python** CV/OSC + fusion; **not** TS triad/gates.
- **`.cursor/rules/alchemist-python-economy.mdc`** — **local Python** (`~/alchemist-tools/`) for bulk JSON/fixtures/indexes so assistants **do not burn LLM tokens** generating data inline; **in-repo** **`tools/validate-offsets.py`** = HARD GATE only; shipped **`pnpm learning:*`** / Node pipelines stay canonical unless the rule says otherwise.

